quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  11,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  11,1,Alif Laaam Raa. yeh woh kitaab hai jis ki ayatain mustahkam hain aur khuday-e hakeem o khabeer ki taraf se bah tafseel bayan kar di gayi hai
  11,2,( woh yeh ) ke khuda ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo aur mein is ki taraf se tum ko dar sunanay wala aur khushkhabri dainay wala hon
  11,3,aur yeh ke apne perwar-digaar se bakhshish mango aur is ke agay tauba karo woh to tum ko aik waqt muqarara taq mata naik se behra mand kere ga aur har sahib buzurag ko is ki buzurgi ( ki daad ) day ga. aur agar rogrdani karo ge to mujhe tumahray baray mein ( qayamat ke ) barray din ke azaab ka dar hai
  11,4,tum ( sab ) ko khuda ki taraf lout kar jana hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  11,5,dekho yeh apne seenon ko dohara ا karte hain taakay khuda se parda karen. sun rakho jis waqt yeh kapron mein lapat kar parte hain ( tab bhi ) woh un ki chhupi aur khuli baton ko jaanta hai. woh to dilon taq ki baton se aagah hai
  11,6,"aur zameen par koi chalne phirnay wala nahi magar is ka rizaq khuda ke zimmay hai woh jahan rehta hai, usay bhi jaanta hai aur jahan sonpa jata hai usay bhi. yeh sab kuch kitaab roshan mein ( likha howa ) hai"
  11,7,aur wohi to hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay din mein banaya aur ( is waqt ) is ka arsh pani par tha. ( tumahray peda karne se ) maqsood yeh hai ke woh tum ko aazamaa_e ke tum mein amal ke lehaaz se kon behtar hai aur agar tum kaho ke tum log marnay ke baad ( zindah karkay ) uthaye jao ge to kafir keh den ge ke yeh to khula jaadoo hai
  11,8,aur agar aik muddat Moueen taq hum un se azaab rok den to kahin ge ke kon si cheez azaab rokay hue hai. dekho jis roz woh un par waqay hoga ( phir ) talnay ka nahi aur jis cheez ke sath yehistehzaakiya karte hain woh un ko ghair le gi
  11,9,aur agar hum ensaan ko apne paas se Nemat bakhsheen phir is se is ko chean len to na umeed ( aur ) nashukara ( hojata ) hai
  11,10,aur agar takleef pounchanay ke baad asayish ka maza chkhayin to ( khush ho kar ) kehta hai ke ( ahaa ) sab skhtyan mujh se daur hogai. be shak woh khusihyan mananay wala ( aur ) fakhr karne wala hai
  11,11,haan jinhon ne sabrkiya aur amal naik kiye. yahi hain jin ke liye bakhshish aur ajre azeemhai
  11,12,shayad tum kuch cheez wahi mein se jo tumahray paas aati hai chore do aur is ( khayaal ) se ke tumhara dil tang ho ke ( kafir ) yeh kehnay lagen ke is par koi khazana kyun nah nazil howa ya is ke sath koi farishta kyun nahi aaya. ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam! tum to sirf nasiyaat karne walay ho. aur khuda har cheez ka nigehbaan hai
  11,13,"yehkiya kehte hain ke is ne quran azkhud bana liya hai? keh do ke agar sachey ho to tum bhi aisi das sortin bana lao aur khuda ke siwa jis jis ko bulaa saktay ho, bulaa bhi lau"
  11,14,agar woh tumhari baat qubool nah karen to jaan lau ke woh khuda ke ilm se utra hai aur yeh ke is ke siwa koi mabood nahi to tumhe bhi islam le aana chahiye
  11,15,jo log duniya ki zindagi aur is ki Zaib o zeenat ke taalib hon hum un ke aamaal ka badla inhen duniya mein hi day dete hain aur is mein un ki haq talfi nahi ki jati
  11,16,"yeh woh log hain jin ke liye akhirat mein aatish ( jahannum ) ke siwa koi cheez nahi aur jo amal unhon ne duniya mein kiye sab barbaad aur jo kuch woh karte rahay, sab zaya"
  11,17,bhala jo log apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se ( roshan ) Daleel rakhtay hon aur un ke sath aik ( aasmani ) gawah bhi is ki janib se ho aur is se pehlay moose ki kitaab ho jo peshwa aur rehmat hai ( tokiya woh quran par imaan nahi layein ge ) yahi log is par imaan laatay hain aur jo koi aur firqoun mein se is se munhkir ho to is ka thikana aag hai. to tum is ( quran ) se shak mein nah hona. yeh tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai lekin aksar log imaan nahi laatay
  11,18,aur is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo khuda par jhoot iftira kere aisay log khuda ke samnay paish kiye jayen ge aur gawah kahin ge ke yahi log hain jinhon ne apne perwar-digaar par jhoot bola tha. sun rakho ke zaalmon par allah ki laanat hai
  11,19,jo khuda ke raste se roktay hain aur is mein kajji chahtay hain aur woh akhirat se bhi inkaar karte hain
  11,20,yeh log zameen mein ( kahin bhaag kar khuda ko ) nahi hara satke aur nah khuda ke siwa koi un ka himayati hai. ( ae paighambar ) un ko dugna azaab diya jaye ga kyunkay yeh ( shiddat kufar se tumhari baat ) nahi sun satke they aur nah ( tum ko ) dekh satke they
  11,21,yahi hain jinhon ne apne tain khasaray mein dala aur jo kuch woh iftirakiya karte they un se jata raha
  11,22,bilashuba yeh log akhirat mein sab se ziyada nuqsaan panay walay hain
  11,23,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik kiye aur apne perwar-digaar ke agay aajzi ki. yahi sahib jannat hain aur hamesha is mein rahen ge
  11,24,dono firqoun ( yani kafir o momin ) ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik andha berha ho aur aik daikhta santa. bhala dono ka haal yaksaa ho sakta hai? phir tum sochte kyun nahi ?
  11,25,aur hum ne Nooh ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja ( to unhon ne un se kaha ) ke mein tum ko khol khol kar dar sunanay aur pegham pohanchanay aaya hon
  11,26,ke khuda ke siwa kisi ki ibadat nah karo. mujhe tumhari nisbat azaab alim ka khauf hai
  11,27,to un ki qoum ke sardar jo kafir they kehnay lagey ke hum tum ko apne hi jaissa aik aadmi dekhte hain aur yeh bhi dekhte hain ke tumahray pairo wohi log hue hain jo hum mein adna darjay ke hain. aur woh bhi raye zahir se ( nah ghauro ta-am-uq se ) aur hum tum mein apne oopar kisi terhan ki fazeelat nahi dekhte balkay tumhe jhoota khayaal karte hain
  11,28,unhon ne kaha ke ae qoum! dekho to agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se Daleel ( roshan ) rakhta hon aur is ne mujhe apne haan se rehmat bakhsh ho jis ki haqeeqat tum se posheeda rakhi gayi hai. tokiya hum is ke liye tumhe majaboor kar saktay hain aur tum ho ke is se nakhush ho rahay ho
  11,29,"aur ae qoum! mein is ( nasiyaat ) ke badlay tum se maal vzr ka khwaahan nahi hon, mera sila to khuda ke zimmay hai aur jo log imaan laaye hain, mein un ko nikaalte wala bhi nahi hon. woh to apne perwar-digaar se milnay walay hain lekin mein daikhta hon ke tum log nadani kar rahay ho"
  11,30,aur baradran millat! agar mein un ko nikaal dun to ( azaab ) khuda se ( bachanay ke liye ) kon meri madad karsaktha hai. bhala tum ghhor kyun nahi karte ?
  11,31,mein nah tum se yeh kehta hon ke mere paas khuda ke khazanay hain aur nah yeh ke mein ghaib jaanta hon aur nah yeh kehta hon ke mein farishta hon aur nah un logon ki nisbat jin ko tum hiqarat ki nazar se dekhte ho yeh kehta hon ke khuda un ko bhalai ( yani aamaal ki jzaye naik ) nahi day ga jo un ke dilon mein hai usay khuda khoob jaanta hai. agar mein aisa kahoon to be insafon mein hon
  11,32,unhon ne kaha ke Nooh tum ne hum se jhagra tokiya aur jhagra bhi bohatkiya. lekin agar sachey ho to jis cheez se hamein darate ho woh hum par laa nazil karo
  11,33,Nooh ne kaha ke is ko khuda hi chahay ga to nazil kere ga. aur tum ( uss ko kisi terhan ) hara nahi satke
  11,34,aur agar mein yeh chahoon ke tumhari khirkhwahi karoon aur khuda yeh chahay woh tumhe gumraah kere to meri khirkhwahi tum ko kuch faida nahi day sakti. wohi tumhara perwar-digaar hai aur tumhe is ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  11,35,kiya yeh kehte hain ke is ( paighambar ) ne yeh quran apne dil se bana liya hai. keh do ke agar mein ne dil se bnalya hai to mere gunah ka wabaal mujh par aur jo gunah tum karte ho is se mein buri alzmh hon
  11,36,"aur Nooh ki taraf wahi ki gayi ke tumhari qoum mein jo log imaan ( lachke ), un ke siwa koi aur imaan nahi laaye ga to jo kaam yeh kar rahay hain un ki wajah se gham nah khao"
  11,37,aur aik kashti hamaray hukum se hamaray rubaroo banaao. aur jo log zalim hain un ke baray mein hum se kuch nah kehna kyunkay woh zaroor ghark kardiye jayen ge
  11,38,to Nooh ne kashti banani shuru kar di. aur jab un ki qoum ke sardar un ke paas se guzarte to un se tamaskhur karte. woh kehte ke agar tum hum se tamaskhur karte ho to jis terhan tum hum se tamaskhur karte ho is terhan ( aik waqt ) hum bhi tum se tamaskhur karen ge
  11,39,aur tum ko jald maloom hojaye ga ke kis par azaab aata hai aur jo usay ruswa kere ga aur kis par hamesha ka azaab nazil hota hai
  11,40,yahan taq ke jab hamara hukum aap_hncha aur tanoor josh maarny laga to hum ne Nooh ko hukum diya ke har qisam ( ke jandaroon ) mein se jora jora ( yani ) do ( do janwar. aik aik nar aur aik aik madah ) le lau aur jis shakhs ki nisbat hukum hochuka hai ( ke halaak hojaye ga ) is ko chore kar apne ghar walon ko jo imaan laya ho is ko kashti mein sawaar kar lau aur un ke sath imaan bohat hi kam log laaye they
  11,41,( Nooh ne ) kaha ke khuda ka naam le kar ( ke isi ke haath mein is ka ) chalna aur theharna ( hai ) is mein sawaar hojao. be shak mera perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  11,42,"aur woh un ko le kar ( tufaan ki ) lehron mein chalne lagi. ( laharenkiya theen ) goya pahar ( they ) is waqt Nooh ne apne betay ko ke jo ( kashti se ) allag tha, puraka ke beta hamaray sath sawaar hoja aur kafiroon mein shaamil nah ho"
  11,43,"is ne kaha ke mein ( abhi ) pahar se ja lagun ga, woh mujhe pani se bachale ga. unhon ne kaha ke aaj khuda ke azaab se koi bachanay wala nahi ( aur nah koi bach sakta hai ) magar jis par khuda reham kere. itnay mein dono ke darmain lehar آحائل hui aur woh doob kar reh gaya"
  11,44,aur hukum diya gaya ke ae zameen apna pani nigal ja aur ae aasman tham ja. to pani khushk hogaya aur kaam tamam kardiya gaya aur kashi koh Jodi par ja thahri. aur keh diya gaya ke be insaaf logon par laanat
  11,45,aur Nooh ne apne perwar-digaar ko puraka aur kaha ke perwar-digaar mera beta bhi mere ghar walon mein hai ( to is ko bhi nijaat day ) tera wada sacha hai aur to sab se behtar haakim hai
  11,46,khuda ne farmaya ke Nooh woh tairay ghar walon mein nahi hai woh to na shaista af-aal hai to jis cheez ki tum ko haqeeqat maloom nahi hai is ke baray mein mujh se sawal hi nah karo. aur mein tum ko nasiyaat karta hon ke nadaan nah bano
  11,47,Nooh ne kaha perwar-digaar mein tujh se panah mangta hon ke aisi cheez ka tujh se sawal karoon jis ki haqeeqat mujhe maloom nahi. aur agar to mujhe nahi bakhshay ga aur mujh par reham nahi kere ga to mein tabah hojaon ga
  11,48,hukum howa ke Nooh hamari taraf se salamti aur barkatoon ke sath ( jo ) tum par aur tumahray sath ki jamaaton par ( nazil ki gayi hain ) utar aao. aur kuch aur jamaten hon gi jin ko hum ( duniya ke fawaid se ) Mahzooz karen ge phir un ko hamari taraf se azaab alim puhanche ga
  11,49,yeh ( halaat ) munhjmala ghaib ki khabron ke hain jo hum tumhari taraf bhaijtay hain. aur is se pehlay nah tum hi un ko jantay they aur nah tumhari qoum ( hi un se waaqif thi ) to sabr karo ke injaam parhaiz garon hi ka ( bhala ) hai
  11,50,"aur hum ne Aad ki taraf un ke bhai Hood ( ko bheja ) unhon ne kaha ke meri qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo, is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. tum ( shirk karkay khuda par ) mehez bohtan bandhtay ho"
  11,51,meri qoum! mein is ( waaz o nasiyaat ) ka tum se kuch sila nahi mangta. mera sila to is ke zimmay hai jis ne mujhe pedakiya. bhala tum samajte kyun nahi ?
  11,52,aur ae qoum! apne perwar-digaar se bakhshish mango phir is ke agay tauba karo. woh tum par aasman se musladhar meen barsaye ga aur tumhari taaqat par taaqat bherhaye ga aur ( dekho ) gunehgaar ban kar rogrdani nah karo
  11,53,woh bolay Hood tum hamaray paas koi Daleel zahir nahi laaye aur hum ( sirf ) tumahray kehnay se nah apne mabodon ko chorney walay hain aur nah tum par imaan laane walay hain
  11,54,hum to yeh samajte hain ke hamaray kisi mabood ne tumhe asaib pouncha kar ( deewana kar ) diya hai. unhon ne kaha ke mein khuda ko gawah karta hon aur tum bhi gawah raho ke jin ko tum ( khuda ka ) shareek banatay ho mein is se bezaar hon
  11,55,( yani jin ki ) khuda ke siwa ( ibadat karte ho to ) tum sab mil kar mere baray mein jo tadbeer ( karni chaho ) karlo aur mujhe mohlat nah do
  11,56,"mein khuda par jo mera aur tumhara ( sab ka ) perwar-digaar hai, bharosa rakhta hon ( zameen par ) jo chalne phirnay wala hai woh is ko chouti se pakdae hue hai. be shak mera perwar-digaar seedhay raste par hai"
  11,57,"agar tum rogrdani karo ge to jo pegham mere haath tumhari taraf bheja gaya hai, woh mein ne tumhe pouncha diya hai. aur mera perwar-digaar tumhari jagah aur logon ko laa basa-ay ga. aur tum khuda ka kuch bhi nuqsaan nahi kar saktay. mera perwar-digaar to har cheez par nigehbaan hai"
  11,58,aur jab hamara hukum azaab aap_hncha to hum ne Hood ko aur jo log un ke sath imaan laaye they un ko apni meharbani se bacha liya. aur un ko azaab shadeed se nijaat di
  11,59,yeh ( wohi ) Aad hain jinhon ne khuda ki nishanion se inkaarkiya aur is ke peghambaroon ki nafarmani ki aur har mutaqabbiro sarkah ka kaha maana
  11,60,to is duniya mein bhi laanat un ke peechay lagi rahay gi aur qayamat ke din bhi ( lagi rahay gi ) dekho Aad ne apne perwar-digaar se kufarkiya. ( aur ) sun rakho Hood ki qoum Aad par phatkaar hai
  11,61,aur smod ki taraf un ke bhai Saleh ko ( bheja ) to unhon ne kaha ke qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. isi ne tum ko zameen se pedakiya aur is mein abadkiya to is se mughfirat mango aur is ke agay tauba karo. be shak mera perwar-digaar nazdeek ( bhi hai aur dua ka ) qubool karne wala ( bhi ) hai
  11,62,"unhon ne kaha ke Saleh is se pehlay hum tum se ( kayi terhan ki ) umeeden rakhtay they ( ab woh munhqita hogai )kiya tum hum ko un cheezon ke poojnay se mana karte ho jin ko hamaray buzurag pujte aeye hain? aur jis baat ki taraf tum hamein bulatay ho, is mein hamein quwwat shuba hai"
  11,63,Saleh ne kaha ae qoum! bhala dekho to agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se khuli Daleel par hon aur is ne mujhe apne haan se ( nabuwat ki ) Nemat bakhsh ho to agar mein khuda ki nafarmani karoon to is ke samnay meri kon madad kere ga? tum to ( kufar ki baton se ) mera nuqsaan karte ho
  11,64,aur yeh bhi kaha ke ae qoum! yeh khuda ki oontni tumahray liye aik nishani ( yani moujza ) hai to is ko chore do ke khuda ki zameen mein ( jahan chahay ) charay aur is ko kisi terhan ki takleef nah dena warna tumhe jald azaab a pakray ga
  11,65,magar unhon ne is ki kunchain kaat dalain. to ( Saleh ne ) kaha ke apne gharon mein tum teen din ( aur ) faida utha lau. yeh wada hai ke jhoota nah hoga
  11,66,jab hamara hukum agaya to hum ne Saleh ko aur jo log un ke sath imaan laaye they un ko apni meharbani se bchalya. aur is din ki ruswai se ( mehfooz rakha ). be shak tumhara perwar-digaar taaqatwar aur zabardast hai
  11,67,aur jin logon ne zulmkiya tha un ko chngharh ( ki soorat mein azaab ) ne aapkrha to woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay
  11,68,goya kabhi un mein basey hi nah they. sun rakho ke smod ne apne perwar-digaar se kufarkiya. aur sun rakho smod par phatkaar hai
  11,69,aur hamaray farishtay ibrahim ke paas basharat le kar aeye to salam kaha. unhon ne bhi ( jawab mein ) salam kaha. abhi kuch waqfa nahi howa tha ke ( ibrahim ) aik bhana howa bitchrha le aeye
  11,70,"jab dekha ke un ke haath khanay ki taraf nahi jatay ( yani woh khana nahi khatay ) to un ko ajnabi samajh kar dil mein khaufkiya. ( firshton ne ) kaha ke khauf nah kiijiye, hum qoum Loot ki taraf ( un ke halaak karne ko ) beje gay hain"
  11,71,"aur ibrahim ki biwi ( jo paas ) khari thi, hans pari to hum ne is ko Ishaq ki aur Ishaq ke baad Yaqoob ki khushkhabri di"
  11,72,is ne kaha ae hai mere bacha hoga? mein to budiya hon aur mere miyan bhi boorhay hain. yeh to barri ajeeb baat hai
  11,73,unhon ne kahakiya tum khuda ki qudrat se taajjub karti ho? ae ahal beeet tum par khuda ki rehmat aur is ki barkaten hain. woh sazawar tareef aur bzrgwar hai
  11,74,jab ibrahim se khauf jata raha aur un ko khushkhabri bhi mil gayi to qoum Loot ke baray mein lagey hum se behas karne
  11,75,"be shak ibrahim barray tahhaamul walay, naram dil aur rujoo karne walay they"
  11,76,ae ibrahim is baat ko jaane do. tumahray perwar-digaar ka hukum aap_hncha hai. aur un logon par azaab anay wala hai jo kabhi nahi talnay ka
  11,77,aur jab hamaray farishtay Loot ke paas aeye to woh un ( ke anay ) se ghumnaak aur tang dil hue aur kehnay lagey ke aaj ka din barri mushkil ka din hai
  11,78,"aur Loot ki qoum ke log un ke paas be thaasha dorrtay hue aeye aur yeh log pehlay hi se feal شنیعkiya karte they. Loot ne kaha ke ae qoum! yeh ( jo ) meri ( qoum ki ) larkiyan hain, yeh tumahray liye ( jaaiz aur ) pak hain. to khuda se daro aur mere mehmanon ke ( baray ) mein meri aabaroo nah کھوؤ.kiya tum mein koi bhi shaista aadmi nahi"
  11,79,woh bolay tum ko maloom hai ke tumhari ( qoum ki ) baityon ki hamein kuch haajat nahi. aur jo hamari gharz hai usay tum ( khoob ) jantay ho
  11,80,Loot ne kaha ae kash mujh mein tumahray muqablay ki taaqat hoti ya kisi mazboot qilay mein panah pakar sakta
  11,81,firshton ne kaha ke Loot hum tumahray perwar-digaar ke farishtay hain. yeh log hargiz tum taq nahi poanch saken ge to kuch raat rahay se apne ghar walon ko le kar chal do aur tum mein se koi shakhs peechay phir kar nah dekhe. magar tumhari biwi ke jo aafat un par parney wali hai wohi is par parre gi. un ke ( azaab ke ) waday ka waqt subah hai. aurkiya subah kuch daur hai ?
  11,82,to jab hamara hukum aaya hum ne is ( bastii ) ko ( ulat kar ) neechay oopar kardiya aur un par pathar ki teh bah teh ( yani pay darpay ) kankariyan barsaaen
  11,83,jin par tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan se nishaan kiye hue they aur woh bastii un zaalmon se kuch daur nahi
  11,84,aur Mudin ki taraf un ke bhai Shoiab ko ( bheja ) to onhon ne kaha ke ae qoum! khuda hi ki ibadat karo ke is ke siwa tumhara koi mabood nahi. aur naap toal mein kami nahkiya karo. mein to tum ko aasooda haal daikhta hon aur ( agar tum imaan nah lao ge to ) mujhe tumahray baray mein aik aisay din ke azaab ka khauf hai jo tum ko ghair kar rahay ga
  11,85,aur qoum! map aur toal insaaf ke sath poori poorikiya karo aur logon ko un ki cheezein kam nah diya karo aur zameen mein kharabi karte nah phiro
  11,86,agar tum ko ( mere kehnay ka ) yaqeen ho to khuda ka diya howa naffa hi tumahray liye behtar hai aur mein tumhara nigehbaan nahi hon
  11,87,unhon ne kaha Shoiabkiya tumhari namaz tumhe yeh sikhati hai ke jin ko hamaray baap dada pujte aeye hain hum un ko tark kar den ya apne maal mein tasarruf karna chahain to nah karen. tum to barray naram dil aur raast baz ho
  11,88,unhon ne kaha ke ae qoum! dekho to agar mein apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se Daleel roshan par hon aur is ne apne haan se mujhe naik rozi di ho ( tokiya mein un ke khilaaf karoon ga? ) aur mein nahi chahta ke jis amar se mein tumhe mana karoon khud is ko karne lagun. mein to jahan taq mujh se hosakay ( tumahray mamlaat ki ) islaah chahta hon aur ( is baray mein ) mujhe tofeq ka milna khuda hi ( ke fazl ) se hai. mein isi par bharosa rakhta hon aur is ki taraf rujoo karta hon
  11,89,aur ae qoum! meri mukhalfat tum se koi aisa kaam nah karaday ke jaisi museebat Nooh ki qoum ya Hood ki qoum ya Saleh ki qoum par waqay hui thi waisi hi museebat tum par waqay ho. aur Loot ki qoum ( ka zamana to ) tum se kuch daur nahi
  11,90,aur apne perwar-digaar se bakhshish mango aur is ke agay tauba karo. be shak mera perwar-digaar reham wala ( aur ) mohabbat wala hai
  11,91,onhon ne kaha ke Shoiab tumhari bohat si baatein hamari samajh mein nahi aatin aur hum dekhte hain ke tum hum mein kamzor bhi ho aur agar tumahray bhai nah hotay to hum tum ko sangsar kar dete aur tum hum par ( kisi terhan bhi ) ghalib nahi ho
  11,92,unhon ne kaha ke qoum!kiya mere bhai bundon ka dabao tum par khuda se ziyada hai. aur is ko tum ne peeth peechay daal rakha hai. mera perwar-digaar to tumahray sab aamaal par ihata kiye hue hai
  11,93,"aur baradran millat! tum apni jagah kaam kiye jao mein ( apni jagah ) kaam kiye jata hon. tum ko anqareeb maloom hojaye ga ke ruswa karne wala azaab kis par aata hai aur jhoota kon hai aur tum bhi intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon"
  11,94,"aur jab hamara hukum aap_hncha to hum ne Shoiab ko aur jo log un ke sath imaan laaye they un ko to apni rehmat se bacha liya. aur jo log zalim they, un ko chngharh ne آدبوچا to woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre reh gay"
  11,95,goya un mein kabhi basey hi nah they. sun rakho ke Mudin par ( waisi hi ) phatkaar hai jaisi smod par phatkaar thi
  11,96,aur hum ne moose ko apni nishanain aur Daleel roshan day kar bheja
  11,97,( yani ) firaon aur is ke sardaro ki taraf. to woh firaon hi ke hukum par chalay. aur firaon ka hukum durust nahi tha
  11,98,woh qayamat ke din apni qoum ke agay agay chalay ga aur un ko dozakh mein ja utaray ga aur jis maqam par woh utaray jayen ge woh bura hai
  11,99,aur is Jahan mein bhi laanat un ke peechay laga di gayi aur qayamat ke din bhi ( peechay lagi rahay gi ). jo inaam un ko mila hai bura hai
  11,100,yeh ( purani ) bustiyon ke thoray se halaat hain jo hum tum se bayan karte hain. un mein se baaz to baqi hain aur baaz ka tehass nehass hogaya
  11,101,aur hum ne un logon par zulm nahikiya balkay unhon ne khud apne ooper zulmkiya. gharz jab tumahray perwar-digaar ka hukum aap_hncha to jin mabodon ko woh khuda ke siwa puraka karte they woh un ke kuch bhi kaam nah aeye. aur tabah karne ke siwa un ke haq mein aur kuch nah kar sakay
  11,102,aur tumhara perwar-digaar jab nafarman bustiyon ko pakra karta hai to is ki pakar isi terhan ki hoti hai. be shak is ki pakar dukh dainay wali aur sakht hai
  11,103,un ( qisson ) mein is shakhs ke liye jo azaab akhirat se daray Ibrat hai. yeh woh din hoga jis mein sab log ikathay kiye jayen ge aur yahi woh din hoga jis mein sab ( khuda ke rubaroo ) haazir kiye jayen ge
  11,104,aur hum is ke laane mein aik waqt Moueen taq takheer kar rahay hain
  11,105,jis roz woh aajay ga to koi mutnaqas khuda ke hukum ke baghair bol bhi nahi sakay ga. phir un mein se kuch badbakht hon ge aur kuch naik bakht
  11,106,to jo badbakht hon ge woh dozakh mein ( daal diye jayen ge ) is mein un ka chalana aur dhaarna hoga
  11,107,"( aur ) jab taq aasman aur zameen hain, isi mein rahen ge magar jitna tumhara perwar-digaar chahay. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jo chahta hai kardaita hai"
  11,108,"aur jo naik bakht hon ge, woh bahisht mein daakhil kiye jayen ge aur jab taq aasman aur zameen hain hamesha isi mein rahen ge magar jitna tumhara perwar-digaar chahay. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar jo chahta hai kardaita hai. aur jo naik bakht hon ge woh bahisht mein daakhil kiye jayen ge ( aur ) jab taq aasman aur zameen hain hamesha isi mein rahen ge. magar jitna tumhara perwar-digaar chahay. yeh ( khuda ki ) bakhshish hai jo kabhi munhqita nahi hogi"
  11,109,to yeh log jo ( ghair khuda ki ) parastish karte hain. is se tum Khuljan mein nah parna. yeh isi terhan parastish karte hain jis terhan pehlay se un ke baap dada parastish karte aeye hain. aur hum un ko un ka hissa poora poora bulaa kam vikasit dainay walay hain
  11,110,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di to is mein ikhtilaafkiya gaya aur agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik baat pehlay nah hochuki hoti to un mein faisla kardiya jata. aur woh to is se quwwat shubhay mein ( parre hue ) hain
  11,111,aur tumhara perwar-digaar un sab ko ( qayamat ke din ) un ke aamaal ka poora poora badla day ga. be shak jo amal yeh karte hain woh is se waaqif hai
  11,112,so ( ae paighambar ) jaissa tum ko hukum hota hai ( is par ) tum aur jo log tumahray sath Taib hue hain qaim raho. aur hadd se tajawaz nah karna. woh tumahray sab aamaal ko dekh raha hai
  11,113,"aur jo log zalim hain, un ki taraf mael nah hona, nahi to tumhe ( dozakh ki ) aag آلپٹے gi aur khuda ke siwa tumahray aur dost nahi hain. agar tum zaalmon ki taraf mael hogaye to phir tum ko ( kahin se ) madad nah mil sakay gi"
  11,114,aur din ke dono suron ( yani subah aur shaam ke auqaat mein ) aur raat ki chand ( pehli ) sa'at mein namaz parha karo. kuch shak nahi ke naikian gunaaho ko daur kar deti hain. yeh un ke liye nasiyaat hai jo nasiyaat qubool karne walay hain
  11,115,aur sabr kiye raho ke khuda naiko karon ka ajar zaya nahi karta
  11,116,"to jo ummatain tum se pehlay guzar chuki hain, un mein aisay hosh mand kyun nah hue jo malik mein kharabi karne se roktay haan ( aisay ) thoray se ( they ) jin ko hum ne un mein se mukhlasi bakhsh. aur jo zalim they woh un hi baton ke peechay lagey rahay jis mein aish o aaram tha aur woh gunaaho mein doobe hue they"
  11,117,aur tumhara perwar-digaar aisa nahi hai ke bustiyon ko jab ke wahan ke bashinday nekokaar hon azrahِ zulm tabah kardey
  11,118,aur agar tumhara perwar-digaar chahta to tamam logon ko aik hi jamaat kardaita lekin woh hamesha ikhtilaaf karte rahen ge
  11,119,magar jin par tumhara perwar-digaar reham kere. aur isi liye is ne un ko pedakiya hai aur tumahray perwar-digaar ka qoul poora hogaya ke mein dozakh ko junoo aur insanon sab se bhar dun ga
  11,120,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) aur payghambaroon ke woh sab halaat jo hum tum se bayan karte hain un se hum tumahray dil ko qaim rakhtay hain. aur un ( qss ) mein tumahray paas haq poanch gaya aur yeh mominon ke liye nasiyaat aur Ibrat hai
  11,121,aur jo log imaan nahi laaye un se keh do ke tum apni jagah amal kiye jao. hum apni jagah amal kiye jatay hain
  11,122,"aur ( natija-ayٴ aamaal ka ) tum bhi intzaar karo, hum bhi intzaar karte hain"
  11,123,aur asmano aur zameen ki chhupi cheezon ka ilm khuda hi ko hai aur tamam umoor ka rujoo isi ki taraf hai. to isi ki ibadat karo aur isi par bharosa rakho. aur jo kuch tum kar rahay ho tumhara perwar-digaar is se be khabar nahi
